Chinese State Councillor Meets With Colgate Palmolive Head
BEIJING , September 21 ( Xinhua ) -- State Councillor Wu Yi met here this afternoon with Reuben Mark , chairman and CEO of the Colgate Palmolive Company of the United States .
She spoke of the company 's more than 100-year history and praised the company 's achievements in China , and said she hopes it will increase exports of goods produced in China and help improve old Chinese enterprises .
Mark said that his company has businesses in over 200 countries and regions and investment in China worth more than 100 million U.S. dollars , and that it will continue to seek Chinese partners for cooperation .
